[12:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'needed specifically for this book. Make sure each world building element is labeled as one of the following categories. Then we have a list of categories: high-level, settings and locations, objects and artifacts, magic systems and technology, if any, because obviously some genres don\'t need that.'

[12:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
