[29:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'doesn\'t do as well with it and Claude will also throttle you earlier because you\'re using up all of its resources by including 20 plus chapters in there. Secondly, you don\'t actually need to have 20 plus chapters in there because'

